{
  "stem": "22979.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in the middle of-- of the tent was a pool, kind of, with the water, dark water.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Had to jump into the water, and dip in the water, the cold water.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a cleansing bath, because we Jews, they said, brought lice to the camp, and we are dirty.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When you just, you know, for a few seconds, dip completely after the shaving.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then they threw at me a-- a Russian uniform.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I have to mention-- before we came, 75,000 Russian POWs were, since 1940, in Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were killed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we got their uniforms.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The uniforms still were stiff from blood.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And you know, those uniforms, those were long blouses-- I got a-- you know-- a long blouse-- and you know how thin I am-- and the pants, you know, like for-- they were here wider-- probably like cavalry with horses wore those-- and I didn't-- no underwear-- nothing.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And wooden clogs.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And one red bowl and a spoon.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That's it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We have to wear it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was thrown at us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The blouse was so big for me, it was all the way down to the floor.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The pants, I pulled up-- were here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I didn't have a choice-- and nothing to-- to hold it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And nothing to cover our head-- no stocking.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we had to line up until all the 1,000 were cleansed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then we could go back to the barrack.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It took, you know, I don't know how long.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Finally, it happened.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "The girls-- we-- I have-- I have my tattoo number-- when I was tattoo-- is 1,173.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I explain you.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "The 1,000 what you have, they were-- we were the first women tattooed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "The 1,000 are the Germans who came from Ravensbruck.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
